#: ../../en/agent-skills.rst:2
msgid "Agent Skills"
msgstr "Agent Skills"

#: ../../en/agent-skills.rst:4
msgid "AnnaAgent includes a public agent skill for LLMs that can operate command-line tools and files. The skill teaches an agent how to install AnnaAgent, configure a workspace, run full seeker initialization, save reusable prompt states, run chat or batch jobs, and troubleshoot model-service failures."
msgstr "AnnaAgent 提供一个公开 agent skill，面向能够操作命令行工具和文件的 LLM。该 skill 会指导 agent 安装 AnnaAgent、配置 workspace、运行完整 seeker 初始化、保存可复用 prompt state、执行 chat 或 batch 任务，并排查模型服务故障。"

#: ../../en/agent-skills.rst:10
msgid "Skill Location"
msgstr "Skill 位置"

#: ../../en/agent-skills.rst:12
msgid "The skill lives in the repository at:"
msgstr "该 skill 位于仓库中的："

